{"tid":2369751,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2021最強女歌手SOLO回歸大戰！IU、BLACKPINK Rosé &Lisa、泫雅、請夏","createTime":"2021-01-17T11:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T13:40:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"de2f6c347e9aa7a505afa35f73195002dfd99090","tid":2369751,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_24125a4508e050d8394da57d381e497b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-17/133065-893733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_24125a4508e050d8394da57d381e497b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-17%2F133065-893733.jpg&h=e074eff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOMG～！每一位實力都超堅強的啊～！！！每一首都超級期待的。TAT<br />\n<br />\n告別了充滿遺憾的2020年，預計從2021年初開始，將會有一場人氣女歌手 SOLO 的回歸大戰即將展開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼因健康問題標題延遲回歸的「金請夏」將重啟發行正規一輯〈Querencia〉，1月19日會率先公開單曲《X》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_53b92725608d93bc27611fef08a1e6c7/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-17/133065-893734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_53b92725608d93bc27611fef08a1e6c7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-17%2F133065-893734.jpg&h=e30479f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼IU 時隔八個月後以新歌《Celebrity》回歸，是第五張正規專輯的先行曲，預計在1月27日公開，而復古風格兼具華麗的預告照，也被網友P成各種迪士尼主題的公主扮相，有興趣的讀者可按此觀看。<br />\n<br />\n經紀公司還特別提到《Celebrity》這首歌是 IU 首次嘗試的類型，預計會帶給大家充滿活力的音樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_584f79469eec06288db62060cf21ea28/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-17/133065-893736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_584f79469eec06288db62060cf21ea28%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-17%2F133065-893736.jpg&h=7c7544d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼作風一向大膽獨樹一格的泫雅，將會在1月28日發表新歌，這次的回歸時隔了1年2個月，2020年原本有計畫回歸，但因健康原因選擇了暫停活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_90c481c6adc72ea77a10fe7ed67d8086/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-17/133065-893737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_90c481c6adc72ea77a10fe7ed67d8086%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-17%2F133065-893737.jpg&h=0defd678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼在全球擁有超高人氣的 BLACKPINK 成員 Ros&eacute; 和 Lisa 也預告了 solo 的消息，雖然還沒公開確切的個人出道時間，但YG娛樂在年底表示：「BLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;、LISA即將發行SOLO曲，正在準備拍攝MV。」相信在年初就能夠有好消息啦！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_067e60153003bb2cbc8b5285994c384e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-17/133065-893738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_067e60153003bb2cbc8b5285994c384e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-17%2F133065-893738.jpg&h=ac38e350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"017b4fbce842e0393c96b8fbd533b1e74847680b","tid":2369751,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"耳朵眼睛享福了..."},{"pid":"361ce4a6ed18dd89215aba3d767f867d62db67d2","tid":2369751,"uid":256796,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:56:10.000Z","msg":"我地彩英準備稱霸solo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef423f9cd33b0d69a53eee0c28b2b7558002466","tid":2369751,"uid":315047,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"IU由kpop二代打到就嚟六代 好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af08eec7554c416d1e25b4fe137280e766c01b9","tid":2369751,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"巧巧天哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6526720c073c954dd6e0b786c2f3f955545228ac","tid":2369751,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af08eec7554c416d1e25b4fe137280e766c01b9","tid":2369751,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":